name: Restaurant Makan E-2
address: Q8FF+PJ4, Jalan Raya, Kintamani, Kec. Kintamani, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: Away from all the tourists, but you still have beautiful views and good food at uninflated tourist prices.
review 2:
Stop here for having lunch when we went to buleleng. The food is decent, they have some other menu (which i forgot to take the photo) the taste just normal to me nothing special. When i was there, there are so many flies flying around. I dont know why. The food price is pretty cheap compared to other restaurant or cafe that offered in Kintamani

My personal observation based on scale 1 to 5, from very bad, bad, okay, good, very good.

Taste: 3/5
Price: 4/5
Parking area: 4/5
Staff: 3/5
Location: 5/5
Recommended: depends, if you travel for a limited budget, i recommend this. But if not, im not sure i can recommend this to you
review 3: Nice little place with good, cheap food and a great view of Mt. Batur, highly recommend! Way better than the tourist traps along the road.
review 4: Great view while enjoying the meal, affordable price. Mujair nyat-nyat is my favourite. Place is okay.
review 5: The fried noodles with vegetables and egg were delicious and the value for money was extremely good.
